JOE HANZEN

“A DJ in a league of his own, he has graced our stage multiple times, and there are there are more to come.

He is a high-energy catalyst who instinctively understands the audience's desires.”

Elisabet, Hotell Toppen

I was born in the cold north of Sweden in late 2001. Growing up, I did not have much, but my passion for music at an early age enriched me more than any money ever could.

I BEGAN WRITING MUSIC AT A VERY EARLY AGE, BANGING EVERYWHERE TO CREATE SOUNDS AND SINGING AS LOUD AS I COULD EVERY DAY.

THROUGH THIS, MY SONGWRITING EVOLVED UNTIL THE POINT WHERE I REALIZED WHEN I WAS FOURTEEN THAT I WANTED TO RELEASE MUSIC OF MY OWN. VERY QUICKLY IT HIT ME AS I BEGAN TINKERING WITH MAGIX MUSIC MAKER THAT MAYBE MUSIC PRODUCTION IS WHAT I WANT TO DO.

I WAS ABSOLUTELY OBSESSED WITH PRODUCING MUSIC FROM THERE.

I kinda realized that I would NEVER EVER be able to let go of the creative control of my music. I found myself PONDERING THE THOUGHT that I would rather have someone else sing the music I write, rather than have someone produce it for me.

I fell absolutely in love with creating electronic music that had an obvious country/folk/bluegrass accent on it.

FAST FORWARD TO TODAY.

I AM A SEMI-TOURING DJ/ARTIST AND ELECTRONIC PRODUCER AND I CANNOT BE MORE GRATEFUL THAT I GET TO DO THIS FOR A LIVING.

DJ and EDM Producer Joe Hanzen had a great debut,

coming from absolutely nowhere and quickly gaining over 50.000 streams on his first song Surrender, only to shortly after release three more energy filled songs with a lot more well on the way.

Now, semi-touring Joe Hanzen from Örnsköldsvik, Sweden, is hell bent on playing at every venue in the world.

The young DJ from Norrland has, so far, experienced everything from broken attendance records and energy packed dance floors to collaborating several times overseas just to get the right vocals on a track.

Joe Hanzen is smashing through expectations, ready to work harder than ever before.

Reading crowds is his middle name, so if you get to see see him play;

Put on your favourite dance shoes, you’re going to have the night of your life.
